    {
      "url": "https://www.ercot.com/services/comm/mkt_notices/W-B030223-01",
      "title": "W-B030223-01 New version of Resource Interconnection Handbook ...",
      "published_date": "2023-03-02T00:00:00.000Z",
      "text": "Market Notice Details\nTo:Notice\\_Operations@lists.ercot.com,NOTICE\\_GENERAL@LISTS.ERCOT.COM\nSent:3/2/23, 3:11 PM\nSubject:W-B030223-01 New version of Resource Interconnection Handbook posted\n**NOTICE DATE:**March 2, 2023\n**NOTICE TYPE:**W-B030223-01 Operations\n**SHORT DESCRIPTION:**New version of Resource Interconnection Handbook posted\n**INTENDED AUDIENCE:**Resource Entities, Interconnecting Entities, and Transmission/Distribution Service Providers\n**DAYS AFFECTED:**March 3, 2023\n**LONG DESCRIPTION:**An updated Resource Interconnection Handbook, version 1.94, has been posted tothe Resource Integrationpage on ERCOT.com. This version includes:\n1. Updates to various sections on requesting an FIS with the latest version of RIOO-IS with Substation Details\n2. RIOO-IS starting a new request as either an IE or a RE\n3. Replacing the term \"RARF\" with \"resource data\" or similar terms\n4. Change to the weatherization reference document\n5. Diagram to show new telemetry required for co-located data c",
      "highlights": [
        "Subject:W-B030223-01 New version of Resource Interconnection Handbook posted\n**NOTICE DATE:**March 2, 2023 **NOTICE TYPE:**W-B030223-01 Operations\n**SHORT DESCRIPTION:**New version of Resource Interconnection Handbook posted **INTENDED AUDIENCE:**Resource Entities, Interconnecting Entities, and Transmission/Distribution Service Providers **DAYS AFFECTED:**March 3, 2023 **LONG DESCRIPTION:**An updated Resource Interconnection Handbook, version 1.94, has been posted tothe Resource Integrationpage on ERCOT.com. This version includes: 1. Updates to various sections on requesting an FIS with the latest version of RIOO-IS with Substation Details 2. RIOO-IS starting a new request as either an IE or a RE 3. Replacing the term \"RARF\" with \"resource data\" or similar terms\n4. Change to the weatherization reference document 5. Diagram to show new telemetry required for co-located data center loads 6. New paragraph on Operation Requirements for Data Center load and/or PUN loads with IRR Generation New appendices have been added to show:\n1. Appendix N to show Resource Status Codes taken from the ICCP Handbook 2020 Other general edits are also included. **CONTACT:**If you have any questions, please contact your ERCOT Account Manager. You may also call the general ERCOT Client Services phone number at (512) 248-3900 or contact ERCOT Client Services via email atClientServices@ercot.com. **If you are receiving email from a public ERCOT distribution list that you no longer wish to receive, please follow this link in order to unsubscribe from this list:[http://lists.ercot"
