cability...........................................................................................................................1 5.2.2 Initiation of Generator Interconnection or Modification.......................................................3 5.2.3  ...    5.2.4 Duty to Update Project Information and Respond to ERCOT and TDSP Requests  ...    5.2.8 Interconnection Agreements and Procedures.........................................................................9 5.2.8.1 Standard Generation Interconnection Agreement for Transmission-Connected Generators............................................................................................................................. 9 5.2.8.2 Interconnection Agreement for Distribution-Connected Generators................................... 10 5.2.8.3 Provisions for Municipally Owned Utilities and Cooperatives............................................ 10 5.2.9 Self-Limiting  ...    5.3 Interconnection and Study Procedures for Large  ...    5.3.1 Security Screening Study  ...    5.4.2 Submission of Interconnection Agreement and TSP and/or DSP Studies and  ...    TABLE OF CONTENTS\nERCOT PLANNING GUIDE – DECEMBER 1, 2024 TOC-3\nPUBLIC  ...    6.8 Resource Registration  ...    9-1 PUBLIC\nERCOT Planning Guide\nSection 1: Overview\nJune 1, 2023\nSECTION 1: TABLE OF CONTENTS ERCOT PLANNING GUIDE – JUNE 1, 2023\nPUBLIC 1 OVERVIEW...............................................................................................................  ...    1.2 PROCESS FOR PLANN"
      ]
